9 on the Richter scale. The system was shut down. It was centered near Hollister, 80 miles southeast of San Francisco in San Benito County.  PDT and registered 6. The quake was felt as far away as Reno, Nev. A 7 reading is a major earthquake, capable of widespread heavy damage. It occurred at 5:04 p. There were no other immediate confirmed reports of deaths or injuries, but ABC-TV and CNN both said some people were injured at Candlestick, where the game was canceled and fans were evacuated. CBS-TV reported one person had been killed on the bridge. 